node.text:
This Hennessey Venom 1000 GT500 Mustang makes 859 rear wheel HP and 669 rear wheel lb-ft torque on our Dynojet chassis dyno using E85. This performance upgrade features a flex fuel tune that also supports 93 Octane.⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠

node.text:
Chevrolet's C7 Corvette Z06 production may be over, but the aftermarket performance upgrades are still strong! Hennessey is proud to offer reliable, blistering performance upgrades for this LT4-platformed machine. This HPE850 performance upgrade is expertly installed and calibrated, supported by world class customer service, and guaranteed with a 2 year / 24k mile warranty.

Learn more: http://hennesseyperformance.com/vehic...​

Up your Z06 to 850 (or 1000!) HP with Hennessey:
979-885-1300 | http://www.HennesseyPerformance.com

node.title: 850 HP Hennessey Corvette Z06 // SIGHTS AND SOUNDS!

Raise your TRX to the next level with Hennessey. Warranty-guaranteed 900 and 1000 HP options available now!
979-885-1300 | http://www.HennesseyPerformance.com

node.text:
1000 HP GT500 Delivered! 

With a thundering 5.2L supercharged V8 and lightning-quick dual-clutch transmission, the Mustang GT500 ranks among the finest of Ford's lineup. But yeah, we think it could use more power. With Hennessey's expertly calibrated, warranty-guaranteed VENOM 1000 upgrade, the Mustang GT500 retains all stock driveability and function while rocketing into the next level of performance capability.

node.text:
1000 HP DURANGO vs C8 CORVETTE // Drag Race Comparison! 

The 2021 Dodge Durango with supercharged 6.2L Hellcat V8 is an incredibly quick 3-row SUV. Of course, Hennessey takes it to the next level with the HPE1000 performance upgrade. How does this 5,710 lb powerhouse now compare to the substantially lighter C8 Corvette? We headed to the @pennzoil Proving Ground for answers.

GIVEAWAY ALERT! 

Here at Hennessey proof is everything! We test all of our vehicles at the Pennzoil Proving Ground Test Track! We are excited to partner up with @pelicanprofessional and @pennzoil to giveaway a one of a kind PELICAN CASE!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We want to hear from YOU! Here is how to enter:⁠⁠
⁠⁠
1. Include your own personal story of proof – whether it’s putting in long hours or preparing for the next race – what is your own #IAmTheProof story? How do you show the proof of your hard work? Post, comment, or tweet your personal proof story using the hashtag: #IAmTheProof⁠⁠
⁠⁠
2. Follow @Pennzoil @PelicanProfessional @john_hennessey_texas and @hennessey_alex_ on all platforms!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We will announce the giveaway winner one week from today! Let the games begin!⁠⁠
